dct_title_s: Jūmanbun no ichi Zu Girubāto Shotō
dct_description_sm: Maps cover Gilbert Islands: Makin, Butaritari, Marakei, Abaiang, Tarawa, Maiana, Abemama, Kuria, Aranuka, Nonouti, [Tabiteuea,] Beru, [Nikunau,] Onotoa, [Tamana, Arorae].
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
Place names in Japanese and English.
Summary of field survey (location, geographical features, population, food and water supply, sanitary conditions, etc.) printed in red on the map.
